{
  "title": "ReFi Roundup #34: 🐼 Merge for Climate, Kernel, Spirals & ReFi Events",
  "slug": "refi-roundup-34-merge-pandas",
  "html": "<p>Happy Merge week ReFi Nation!</p><p>In this week's edition of ReFi roundup, we'll touch on a few headline stories, feature a handful of new ReFi jobs and highlight some upcoming ReFi events all around the world. </p><ul><li>Ethereum merged to Proof of Stake! 🌎 🐼</li><li>Merge 4 Climate launched it's call to offset historical emissions 📢💨</li><li>Klima removes HFC-23 credits from BCT 💪</li><li>Kernel kicked off Block 7 with Niran from Panvala and a special guest... 🤩</li><li>Spirals Protocol <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/refi-deep-dive-spirals-protocol/\">deep dive</a> on ReFi Podcast 🌀</li></ul><p>Also, ReFi got a nice feature in Fred Wilson's daily blog AVC (founder of USV), which is definitely worth a read!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"es\" dir=\"ltr\">Regenerative Finance (ReFi) <a href=\"https://t.co/W17GnAm3sc\">https://t.co/W17GnAm3sc</a></p>&mdash; avc (@avc) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/avc/status/1569268424731140098?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">September 12, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-22.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1639\" height=\"757\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-22.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-22.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/09/image-22.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-22.png 1639w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h2 id=\"ethereum-merged-to-pos-%F0%9F%8C%8E-%F0%9F%90%BC\">Ethereum Merged to PoS! 🌎 🐼</h2><p>It was such an incredible coordination spectacle to witness the merge from Ethereum Proof of Work to Proof of Stake. I enjoyed the moment with both of my children and was delighted to see a smooth transition—and of course the occasional panda 🐼...</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://eth-4-climate.github.io/merge4climate/\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Celebrate the merge!</a></div><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-19.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1754\" height=\"1590\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-19.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-19.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/09/image-19.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-19.png 1754w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h2 id=\"merge-4-climate-call-to-action-%F0%9F%93%A2%F0%9F%92%A8\">Merge 4 Climate call to action 📢💨</h2><p>A community of ReFi activists are petitioning to offset the historical emissions of Ethereum Proof of Work, with an estimated 18 million tons of carbon dioxide emissions. Founding signatories include BICOWG, KlimaDAO, Toucan, Gitcoin, Zero Labs, Helios, Regen Network &amp; disCarbon. Let's take action and get these emissions out of our atmosphere! 🏭</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://mirror.xyz/eth4climate.eth\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Sign the petition</a></div><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-21.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"769\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-21.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-21.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/09/image-21.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-21.png 2018w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h2 id=\"kernel-block-7-kick-off-with-niran-from-panvala-and-special-guest-%F0%9F%A4%A9\">Kernel Block 7 Kick-off With Niran from Panvala and special guest... 🤩</h2><p>My good friend johnx25bd often says, the best people always seem to come from Kernel. Founded by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/vsinghdothings\">Vivek Singh</a> (co-founder of Gitcoin), it's an incredible community of builders, artists, entrepreneurs and visionaries who work together over an 8-week period across several guilds to make their journey into web3.</p><p>We were stoked to hear from the brilliant <a href=\"https://twitter.com/niran\">Niran</a> from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/PanvalaHQ\">Panvala</a> about the power of communities to change the world and their product vision for doing so... and then Vitalik came by to wish us all a happy Merge day and celebrate the opening of Block 7! </p><p>Such a cool community, grateful to be apart of this cohort.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">To wrap up my <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/EthereumMerge?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#EthereumMerge</a> day, just had an amazing <a href=\"https://twitter.com/KERNEL0x?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@KERNEL0x</a> fireside with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/niran?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@niran</a> from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/PanvalaHQ?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@PanvalaHQ</a> on harnessing the power of community to change the world.<br><br>Tokens and NFTs are the core building blocks we need.<br><br>Then <a href=\"https://twitter.com/VitalikButerin?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@VitalikButerin</a> came in to say hey 👋 <a href=\"https://t.co/U8Px3E0VU4\">pic.twitter.com/U8Px3E0VU4</a></p>&mdash; jE 🪩 #GR15! (@climateXcrypto) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto/status/1570453567475187713?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">September 15, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://kernel.community/\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Check out Kernel</a></div><h2 id=\"klima-removes-hfc-23-credits-from-bct\">Klima removes HFC-23 credits from BCT</h2><p>Strong move from KlimaDAO taking 672k problematic credits from the BCT pool. Significantly improves the optics of BCT.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Following a vote by community members with 83% approval, KlimaDAO has removed 672,000 HFC-23 credits from the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%24BCT&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">$BCT</a> pool.<br><br>Removing these phased-out credits from KlimaDAO’s ecosystem ensures that their environmental benefit cannot be claimed.<a href=\"https://t.co/ensm5f65Za\">https://t.co/ensm5f65Za</a></p>&mdash; KlimaDAO (🌳,🌳) (@KlimaDAO) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/KlimaDAO/status/1570757205082927105?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">September 16, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/pUrDfr69X4w?start=24&feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen title=\"ReFi Podcast S2 E7: Climate Impact Staking with Helena and Doug from Spirals Protocol\"></iframe></figure><h2 id=\"spirals-on-refi-podcast\">Spirals on ReFi Podcast </h2><p>We were super grateful to publish our episode covering the amazing progress of Spirals Protocol to build regenerative infrastructure for Proof of Stake blockchains. Both Helena and Doug are core members of the ReFi community and we're super excited about their protocol and the wonderful network of founders coming around their Solar Punk vision of the future.</p><h3 id=\"listen-%F0%9F%A6%BB\">Listen 🦻</h3><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://pod.fo/e/13ef75\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">ReFi Podcast</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">In this episode of ReFi Podcast, John and Simar are joined by Helena and Doug, and they really dig down on everything Spirals Protocol, which uses yield generated from staking on Celo and directs t...</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://pod.fo/assets/icons/android-icon-192x192.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">podfollow</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://podfollow.com/1609683147/episode/d31b81cd528a527b20b310b7ac7994da7aeb9e48/social?v&#x3D;5&amp;pcv&#x3D;1\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><h3 id=\"read-%F0%9F%91%87%F0%9F%8F%BD\">Read 👇🏽</h3><p>Big thanks to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/0xPhaedrus\">Phaedrus</a> for putting together yet another fantastic deep dive!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"__GHOST_URL__/refi-deep-dive-spirals-protocol/\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">ReFi Deep Dive: Spirals Protocol</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">TL;DRFounded in May, 2022, Spirals Protocol is a new ReFi project launching soon on Celo, currently in closed Beta. They are a self-styled “flywheel of regenerative capital creation”, that aims to support on-the-ground regenerative projects by redirecting unrealized yield to a climate impact fund i…</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"__GHOST_URL__/favicon.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">ReFi DAO Blog</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">Phaedrus</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/S2_EP7_YT_Thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://podcast.refidao.com/\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Subscribe to ReFi Podcast</a></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-dark\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-jobs\">ReFi jobs</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"find-your-next-job-at-a-leading-refi-venture\">Find your next job at a leading ReFi venture</h3></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://refijobs.com/job/660639-community-manager-carbonpath\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-10.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1424\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-10.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-10.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-10.png 1424w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://refijobs.com/job/631678-head-of-marketing-impactscope\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-11.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1424\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-11.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-11.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-11.png 1424w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://refijobs.com/job/550518-smart-contract-developer-menthol-protocol\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-9.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1428\" height=\"328\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-9.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-9.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-9.png 1428w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-12.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1428\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-12.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-12.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-12.png 1428w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-13.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1432\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-13.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-13.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-13.png 1432w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-dark\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-events\">ReFi events</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"get-your-refi-on-in-person-and-online-%F0%9F%95%BA%F0%9F%8F%BC\">Get your ReFi on in-person and online 🕺🏼</h3></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">On Friday Sep 23 at 08.00 PDT we&#39;ll host a Regen Capital Roundtable in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiDAOist?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ReFiDAOist</a> for founders looking to better understand the VC landscape in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a>.<br><br>We&#39;ll hear from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/KristinEIise?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@KristinEIise</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/edwalters?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@edwalters</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/davidjrodriguez?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@davidjrodriguez</a> about their thesis, market insights &amp; tips for founders. <br><br>1/ 8 <a href=\"https://t.co/E5PEmCTjOB\">pic.twitter.com/E5PEmCTjOB</a></p>&mdash; jE 🪩 #GR15! (@climateXcrypto) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto/status/1570744892607037441?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">September 16, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"regen-capital-roundtable-sep-23\">Regen Capital Roundtable Sep 23</h2><p>If you're a founder or investor in the ReFi space, join us in the ReFi DAO Discord for a roundtable conversation with three of the top investors at the intersection of climate and crypto. Should be a blast!</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/qTB9JTah?event&#x3D;1009200675869171734\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Join us</a></div><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-15.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-15.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-15.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-15.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>-</figcaption></figure><h2 id=\"refi-cameroon-sep-1724\">ReFi Cameroon Sep 17 - 24</h2><p>GoodDollar is hosting a week-long event in Cameroon as apart of the ReFi Spring event series. If you missed the first couple days but are in the area, definitely go check it out! Tickets are free...</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://dandelion.earth/events/6320f5bea9716900101f1599\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Grab your free ticket</a></div><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-17.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-17.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-17.png 800w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h2 id=\"refi-uganda-oct-1\">ReFi Uganda Oct 1</h2><p>Jonathan Olwenyi of Ayowecca Uganda, is hosting an event about using crypto to deliver climate solutions, education and training to local farmers. Please, consider making a donation to support the effort of this amazing community via <a href=\"https://t.co/aesxbVvcQc\">Gitcoin GR15</a> or <a href=\"https://opencollective.com/ayoweccauganda\">Open Collective</a>. </p><p>If you're in the area, <a href=\"https://dandelion.earth/events/62f9636c7ec8ea000beded6c\">grab a free ticket</a>!</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://gitcoin.co/grants/4029/agrofrostry-climate-change-ecosystems-and-forests\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Support this event</a></div><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-18.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\"></figure><h2 id=\"refi-barichara-oct-3%E2%80%937-bogota-columbia\">ReFi Barichara, Oct 3–7 | Bogota, Columbia</h2><p>ReFi Practitioners and Earth Regenerators from around the world are gathering in Barichara, Colombia, for a transformative collaboration in the design and creation of ReFi tools applied to the regeneration of an entire bioregion.</p><p>This event will take place October 3-7, 2022, in between two major web3/crypto conferences happening in Colombia:</p><ul><li>Cosmoverse Medellín (Sept 26th-28th)</li><li>ReFi Barichara (OcT 3rd - 7th)</li><li>Devcon Bogotá (Oct. 11th-14th)</li></ul><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://dandelion.earth/events/62f3b29e2c11d600125dc6dc\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Get your ticket</a></div><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-14.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1490\" height=\"740\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/image-14.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/image-14.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/09/image-14.png 1490w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h2 id=\"future-horizon-lisbon\">Future Horizon Lisbon</h2><p>Our friends at Future Horizon are hosting a four-day event in Lisbon from October 26–29 2022. It's invite-only, so request yours below and join the amazing ReFi community forming in Portugal and beyond.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://futurehorizon.to/events/fh20224/\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Request an invite</a></div>",
